summary: Makes your character very powerful and have the best items, tonnes of gold and lockpicks.
descriptionHtml:
This mod: 
Makes you level 255 
Have level 100 in all skills and master all perks.
Gives you all Dragon Amours (Light and Heavy), and all daedric weapons including 10,000 daedric arrows
Gives you 10,000 dragon souls.

Installation-
Place god.txt in the skyrim directory.

Use- 
Open console commands and type: bat god
author: Kinglazy
